{"tid":1328464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊左差唔多7年，親眼睇住佢跟人走","createTime":"2019-07-18T02:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:58:34.000Z","uid":254158,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"36622bcae80a3f4e72a974820a64d067a839007e","tid":1328464,"uid":254158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"我知道已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n你話佢仲掛住我 仲未放低我<br />\n但係你會慢慢放低 叫我乖<br />\n聽到呢句真係好痛<br />\n<br />\n一齊左咁耐<br />\n最痛苦既係行到邊到都有同你既回憶<br />\n<br />\n我同你講「祝你幸福」果陣你知唔知我有幾心痛<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試用工作麻醉自己<br />\n每晚放工盡放搵朋友陪<br />\n但係得返自己一個既時候 仲係忍唔住會諗起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人陪我吹下水分擔下"},{"pid":"3aad41e2f6c13c8c544293a23d5f8ddff14c3014","tid":1328464,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"一時又你一時又佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcd635270605160a9833f4592a4e0524a6080f1","tid":1328464,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"將精力放在反送中<br />\n7.21巴打上前線吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n令自己人生有新目的<br />\n自然會忘記舊事"},{"pid":"42613c6d768e3336b3be70b88363242c2da26ac2","tid":1328464,"uid":249883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"721 金鍾見"},{"pid":"206c360c3ab1008be976f4fa249f31b352f34b1c","tid":1328464,"uid":264062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"講幾多都無用真心要用時間沖淡<br />\n不過要搵人吹水可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9fbb87ba9259ea0be2afa378280f61479ab57","tid":1328464,"uid":53516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif